(81, 1, '2018-12-16 20:09:21', '2018-12-16 20:09:21', '&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-250 size-medium\" src=\"http://toyotires.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/overview-300x34.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"34\" />\n\n&nbsp;\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>WHAT WE DO</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Armstrong Enterprises Company,Inc. specializes in importing quality tires and construction materials and distributing them nationwide.</span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>EXPERIENCE</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have dedicated more than half a century to excelling in the importation and distribution business.</span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>CUSTOMER SATISFACTION</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We strive to give our customers the best and the latest selections from a wide selection of premium products.</span></p>\n\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>WAREHOUSING</strong></h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We take pride our well-maintenance warehousing facility, which stands among the largest in the tire industry.</span></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-260\" src=\"http://toyotires.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Untitled-2-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"185\" height=\"47\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To make our tires and construction materials competitive with other leading products in the country.</span>\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-262\" src=\"http://toyotires.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Untitled-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"185\" height=\"47\" />\n\n<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Integrity, Honesty, Loyalty, Fairness, Respect, and Ethics are of utmost importance.</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong>CUSTOMER SATISFACTION: <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Our future depends on helping our customers become successful. We are proactive, offering expert knowledge and practical solutions.</span></strong>\n\n<strong>WORK ETCHIC: </strong><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We foster a culture that promotes excellent performance, teamwork, leadership and growth.</span>\n\n<strong>PROFESSIONALISM:<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We establish the best business relationship with our customers. Above all, we deliver on our promises.</span></strong>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-266\" src=\"http://toyotires.localhost/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/Untitled-4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"185\" height=\"40\" />\n\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-autosave-v1', '', '', '2018-12-16 20:09:21', '2018-12-16 20:09:21', '', 17, 'http://demo.toyotires.org/2018/10/12/17-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(82, 1, '2018-10-12 06:19:05', '2018-10-12 06:19:05', '<div>\r\n<div>&lt;h5 class=\"title\"&gt;SERVICES, STYLE, AND REALLY GREAT TIRES&lt;/h5&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                    Established in 1966, Toyo Tire U.S.A. Corp. represents the innovation, quality, performance, and excellent service that Toyo Tires has</div>\r\n<div>                                    delivered worldwide for more than 70 years.</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                    We offer a complete selection of premium replacement tires for nearly every make and model including light trucks, SUVs,</div>\r\n<div>                                    high performance cars, and luxury vehicles, as well as commercial trucks. Many of these tires are built here in the United States</div>\r\n<div>                                    at our state-of-the-art factory in Bartow County, Georgia.</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=\"assets/img/toyo-logo.png\" alt=\"\"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                    On October 1, 2007, Toyo Tires unified our brand logos, which previously varied by segment. We have decided to unify our brand logos</div>\r\n<div>                                    in order to strengthen our brand on a global scale and to energize our marketing activities by presenting a uniform brand image.</div>\r\n<div>                                    Vivid blue of Toyo Tires logo conveys an impression of youth.</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=\"assets/img/driven-to-perform.png\" alt=\"\"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;We introduced our brand statement “driven to perform” on May 20, 2008.&lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n<div>                                &lt;p&gt;Logotype of our statement symbolizes loyalty and spirit of innovation.</div>\r\n<div>                                    &lt;br&gt;The figure of expresses inspiration.&lt;/p&gt;</div>\r\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-12 06:19:05', '2018-10-12 06:19:05', '', 17, 'http://demo.toyotires.org/2018/10/12/17-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
