(229, 1, '2017-10-27 16:03:25', '2017-10-27 16:03:25', 'Hyogo, Japan, – Octorber 27, 2017 – Toyo Tire &amp; Rubber Co., Ltd. (HQ: Itami, Hyogo Prefecture, President: Takashi Shimizu) announced that the new Mazda CX-8 crossover SUV with three-row seating, scheduled for release in Japan on December 14, 2017 by Mazda Motor Corporation, will be mounted with TOYO TIRES ’s PROXES R46 tires. (Tire size: 225/55 R19 99V)\r\n\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-230\" src=\"http://toyotires.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img_001-e1509083629149-300x143.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"143\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Letf: PROXES R46 /Right:  Fully mounted Mazda CX-8\r\n※Image of the SUV in this release is provided with the permission of Mazda Motor Corporation.\r\nReuse or reproduction of the image is expressly prohibited.</p>\r\nThe PROXES R46 tires are based on TOYO TIRES’s unique material design technology, “Nano Balance Technology”. As the Mazda CX-8 is set to be the most important model of Mazda’s SUV lineup for Japan, the tires were chosen to meet the new model’s demand for durability, superior environmental performance, and low noise level. TOYO TIRES have previously been chosen in Mazda’s SUV category for use on the CX-3 and CX-5 models. Toyo Tire &amp; Rubber Co., Ltd.’s midterm management plan “Midterm ’17” calls for truck/SUV/CUV tires to occupy a 50% ratio of global new-vehicle tire sales by 2020.\r\n<div class=\"newsContactArea\">\r\n<div class=\"newsContactAreaInner\">\r\n\r\n<strong>TOYO TIRE &amp; RUBBER CO., LTD.</strong> CORPORATE COMMUNICATIONS PLANNING\r\nHyogo Head office Telephone: +81-72-789-9100 Facsimile: +81-72-773-3272\r\nTokyo office Telephone: +81-3-5822-6621 Facsimile: +81-3-3865-2240\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'PROXES R46 tires to be used on the new Mazda CX-8', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'proxes-r46-tires-to-be-used-on-the-new-mazda-cx-8', '', '', '2018-12-16 18:01:17', '2018-12-16 18:01:17', '', 0, 'http://toyotires.org/?p=229', 0, 'post', '', 0),
